properties.Title: Special Weather Statement In Effect
properties.Summary:
Description: Very cold temperatures and wind chills are expected. Coldest wind chills: generally -30 to -20 except -35 over the Great Northern Peninsula. Maximum winds: northwesterly 50 km/h with gusts to 70. Locations: Newfoundland. Time span: tonight until Saturday morning.
